Ivan Linow https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivan_Linow 0 Ivan Linow (born Jānis Linaus; November 21, 1888 – November 11, 1940), also known as Jack Linow, was a Latvian-born American wrestler, who would go on to become a character actor in American films during the silent and early sound film eras.
